						<p>On another pillar in Vishṇu temple in the village.</p>						

						<p>Fragmentary. Registers the grant of two perpetual lamps by Viśvēśvara-Peggaḍa to the temple of Muktēśvara. In characters of the 13th century A.D.</p>						

