<!--<h4>First Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/><unclear>vi</unclear>śvēśvarapeggaḍaṁgā 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ru peṭṭina Akhaṁ 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ḍa dīpālu reṁṭikini 
<lb n="4"/>yī [Ūru] Annipeddi 
<lb n="5"/>ṁgāri koḍku sōmaya 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>vaśamunanu komma 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ranu paḍumaṭi po 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>lāna Emalāna 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>lōna mukteśvara 
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="10"/>munnu Āyuse 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ri lakṣaṇāna Elū 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ṁḍa cēnu puṭṭuṁḍu 
<lb n="13"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> na <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> da <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> yu 
<lb n="14"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ru sa <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="15"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ḍa <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> mūṁḍu 
<lb n="16"/>puṭlu lekha 3 
<lb n="17"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> polamulōnu ca 
</p>

<p>This inscription is not connected with the first face.</p>

